  Note: The workflow is triggered by tag names matching `v*` and runs with `contents: write`, making tag-name injection security-sensitive for release integrity.

github/workflows/release.yml (L57 to 63)
  Note: The newly added step embeds `${{ github.ref_name }}` directly into a PowerShell double-quoted string, allowing a crafted tag name containing quote and statement separators to execute commands.

